{
  "video_id": "BXcFEhl7ynM",
  "title": "Can a robot pass a university entrance exam? | Noriko Arai",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 13140.0,
      "end_time": 16674.0,
      "text": "Today, I&#39;m going to talk about AI and us."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 18206.0,
      "end_time": 20349.0,
      "text": "AI researchers have always said"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 20373.0,
      "end_time": 22967.0,
      "text": "that we humans do not need to worry,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 22991.0,
      "end_time": 26570.0,
      "text": "because only menial jobs will be taken over by machines."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 27274.0,
      "end_time": 28877.0,
      "text": "Is that really true?"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 30365.0,
      "end_time": 34192.0,
      "text": "They have also said that AI will create new jobs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 34216.0,
      "end_time": 37627.0,
      "text": "so those who lose their jobs will find a new one."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 38264.0,
      "end_time": 39619.0,
      "text": "Of course."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 39643.0,
      "end_time": 41815.0,
      "text": "But the real question is:"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 41839.0,
      "end_time": 45944.0,
      "text": "How many of those who may lose their jobs to AI"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 45968.0,
      "end_time": 48457.0,
      "text": "will be able to land a new one,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 48481.0,
      "end_time": 54331.0,
      "text": "especially when AI is smart enough to learn better than most of us?"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 55397.0,
      "end_time": 57582.0,
      "text": "Let me ask you a question:"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 58666.0,
      "end_time": 60464.0,
      "text": "How many of you think"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 60488.0,
      "end_time": 66582.0,
      "text": "that AI will pass the entrance examination of a top university by 2020?"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 67836.0,
      "end_time": 70292.0,
      "text": "Oh, so many. OK."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 70317.0,
      "end_time": 74675.0,
      "text": "So some of you may say, \"Of course, yes!\""
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 75369.0,
      "end_time": 77503.0,
      "text": "Now singularity is the issue."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 78590.0,
      "end_time": 81685.0,
      "text": "And some others may say, \"Maybe,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 81709.0,
      "end_time": 86217.0,
      "text": "because AI already won against a top Go player.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 87213.0,
      "end_time": 90893.0,
      "text": "And others may say, \"No, never. Uh-uh.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 92195.0,
      "end_time": 95788.0,
      "text": "That means we do not know the answer yet, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 96268.0,
      "end_time": 101228.0,
      "text": "So that was the reason why I started Todai Robot Project,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 101252.0,
      "end_time": 105124.0,
      "text": "making an AI which passes the entrance examination"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 105148.0,
      "end_time": 107737.0,
      "text": "of the University of Tokyo,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 107761.0,
      "end_time": 110298.0,
      "text": "the top university in Japan."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 111464.0,
      "end_time": 114120.0,
      "text": "This is our Todai Robot."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 116131.0,
      "end_time": 121941.0,
      "text": "And, of course, the brain of the robot is working in the remote server."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 122747.0,
      "end_time": 126969.0,
      "text": "It is now writing a 600-word essay"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 126993.0,
      "end_time": 131112.0,
      "text": "on maritime trade in the 17th century."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 131136.0,
      "end_time": 132900.0,
      "text": "How does that sound?"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 134113.0,
      "end_time": 138217.0,
      "text": "Why did I take the entrance exam as its benchmark?"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 139980.0,
      "end_time": 143839.0,
      "text": "Because I thought we had to study the performance of AI"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 143863.0,
      "end_time": 145977.0,
      "text": "in comparison to humans,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 146100.0,
      "end_time": 148861.0,
      "text": "especially on the skills and expertise"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 148885.0,
      "end_time": 152972.0,
      "text": "which are believed to be acquired only by humans"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 152997.0,
      "end_time": 155332.0,
      "text": "and only through education."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 155782.0,
      "end_time": 159825.0,
      "text": "To enter Todai, the University of Tokyo,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 159849.0,
      "end_time": 164269.0,
      "text": "you have to pass two different types of exams."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 164294.0,
      "end_time": 168540.0,
      "text": "The first one is a national standardized test"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 168780.0,
      "end_time": 170481.0,
      "text": "in multiple-choice style."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 170505.0,
      "end_time": 172960.0,
      "text": "You have to take seven subjects"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 172984.0,
      "end_time": 174939.0,
      "text": "and achieve a high score --"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 174963.0,
      "end_time": 179734.0,
      "text": "I would say like an 85 percent or more accuracy rate --"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 179759.0,
      "end_time": 183845.0,
      "text": "to be allowed to take the second stage written test"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 183870.0,
      "end_time": 186290.0,
      "text": "prepared by Todai."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 186994.0,
      "end_time": 192311.0,
      "text": "So let me first explain how modern AI works,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 192335.0,
      "end_time": 195404.0,
      "text": "taking the \"Jeopardy!\" challenge as an example."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 197539.0,
      "end_time": 200618.0,
      "text": "Here is a typical \"Jeopardy!\" question:"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 200642.0,
      "end_time": 205103.0,
      "text": "\"Mozart&#39;s last symphony shares its name with this planet.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 206195.0,
      "end_time": 210208.0,
      "text": "Interestingly, a \"Jeopardy!\" question always asks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 210232.0,
      "end_time": 213560.0,
      "text": "always ends with \"this\" something:"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 213584.0,
      "end_time": 216411.0,
      "text": "\"this\" planet, \"this\" country,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 216435.0,
      "end_time": 219430.0,
      "text": "\"this\" rock musician, and so on."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 219670.0,
      "end_time": 223366.0,
      "text": "In other words, \"Jeopardy!\" doesn&#39;t ask many different types of questions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 223390.0,
      "end_time": 225226.0,
      "text": "but a single type,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 225251.0,
      "end_time": 227787.0,
      "text": "which we call \"factoid questions.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 228975.0,
      "end_time": 231142.0,
      "text": "By the way, do you know the answer?"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 233980.0,
      "end_time": 238350.0,
      "text": "If you do not know the answer and if you want to know the answer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 238590.0,
      "end_time": 239346.0,
      "text": "what would you do?"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 240160.0,
      "end_time": 243292.0,
      "text": "You Google, right? Of course."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 243316.0,
      "end_time": 244796.0,
      "text": "Why not?"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 244820.0,
      "end_time": 248412.0,
      "text": "But you have to pick appropriate keywords"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 248436.0,
      "end_time": 252800.0,
      "text": "like \"Mozart,\" \"last\" and \"symphony\" to search."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 253462.0,
      "end_time": 255862.0,
      "text": "The machine basically does the same."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 256457.0,
      "end_time": 261117.0,
      "text": "Then this Wikipedia page will be ranked top."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 261839.0,
      "end_time": 263748.0,
      "text": "Then the machine reads the page."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 263772.0,
      "end_time": 264943.0,
      "text": "No, uh-uh."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 265470.0,
      "end_time": 268932.0,
      "text": "Unfortunately, none of the modern AIs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 268956.0,
      "end_time": 272924.0,
      "text": "including Watson, Siri and Todai Robot,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 272948.0,
      "end_time": 274609.0,
      "text": "is able to read."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 275437.0,
      "end_time": 279237.0,
      "text": "But they are very good at searching and optimizing."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 280158.0,
      "end_time": 282181.0,
      "text": "It will recognize"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 282866.0,
      "end_time": 285801.0,
      "text": "that the keywords \"Mozart,\" \"last\" and \"symphony\""
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 285825.0,
      "end_time": 288728.0,
      "text": "are appearing heavily around here."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 289790.0,
      "end_time": 294165.0,
      "text": "So if it can find a word which is a planet"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 294189.0,
      "end_time": 297837.0,
      "text": "and which is co-occurring with these keywords,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 297861.0,
      "end_time": 299849.0,
      "text": "that must be the answer."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 300762.0,
      "end_time": 305948.0,
      "text": "This is how Watson finds the answer \"Jupiter,\" in this case."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 308433.0,
      "end_time": 312482.0,
      "text": "Our Todai Robot works similarly, but a bit smarter"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 312506.0,
      "end_time": 315744.0,
      "text": "in answering history yes-no questions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 316560.0,
      "end_time": 322223.0,
      "text": "like, \"&#39;Charlemagne repelled the Magyars.&#39; Is this sentence true or false?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 323181.0,
      "end_time": 327253.0,
      "text": "Our robot starts producing a factoid question,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 327278.0,
      "end_time": 332177.0,
      "text": "like: \"Charlemagne repelled [this person type]\" by itself."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 332995.0,
      "end_time": 337727.0,
      "text": "Then, \"Avars\" but not \"Magyars\" is ranked top."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 338357.0,
      "end_time": 341406.0,
      "text": "This sentence is likely to be false."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 342772.0,
      "end_time": 347632.0,
      "text": "Our robot does not read, does not understand,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 348335.0,
      "end_time": 352479.0,
      "text": "but it is statistically correct in many cases."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 354147.0,
      "end_time": 356655.0,
      "text": "For the second stage written test,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 356679.0,
      "end_time": 361784.0,
      "text": "it is required to write a 600-word essay like this one:"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 361809.0,
      "end_time": 364870.0,
      "text": "[Discuss the rise and fall of the maritime trade"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 364111.0,
      "end_time": 366533.0,
      "text": "in East and Southeast Asia in the 17th century ...]"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 366557.0,
      "end_time": 367944.0,
      "text": "and as I have shown earlier,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 367968.0,
      "end_time": 372162.0,
      "text": "our robot took the sentences from the textbooks and Wikipedia,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 372186.0,
      "end_time": 374147.0,
      "text": "combined them together,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 374171.0,
      "end_time": 377790.0,
      "text": "and optimized it to produce an essay"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 377814.0,
      "end_time": 380210.0,
      "text": "without understanding a thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 380450.0,
      "end_time": 381782.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 381806.0,
      "end_time": 386700.0,
      "text": "But surprisingly, it wrote a better essay"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 386725.0,
      "end_time": 388286.0,
      "text": "than most of the students."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 388310.0,
      "end_time": 390701.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 390725.0,
      "end_time": 392254.0,
      "text": "How about mathematics?"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 393354.0,
      "end_time": 396512.0,
      "text": "A fully automatic math-solving machine"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 396536.0,
      "end_time": 398167.0,
      "text": "has been a dream"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 398191.0,
      "end_time": 402869.0,
      "text": "since the birth of the word \"artificial intelligence,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 403785.0,
      "end_time": 409792.0,
      "text": "but it has stayed at the level of arithmetic for a long, long time."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 411530.0,
      "end_time": 416880.0,
      "text": "Last year, we finally succeeded in developing a system"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 416904.0,
      "end_time": 422770.0,
      "text": "which solved pre-university-level problems from end to end,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 422101.0,
      "end_time": 423363.0,
      "text": "like this one."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 425648.0,
      "end_time": 429650.0,
      "text": "This is the original problem written in Japanese,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 429674.0,
      "end_time": 434700.0,
      "text": "and we had to teach it 2,000 mathematical axioms"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 434950.0,
      "end_time": 436869.0,
      "text": "and 8,000 Japanese words"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 436893.0,
      "end_time": 441450.0,
      "text": "to make it accept the problems written in natural language."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 442234.0,
      "end_time": 445775.0,
      "text": "And it is now translating the original problems"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 445800.0,
      "end_time": 448939.0,
      "text": "into machine-readable formulas."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 450578.0,
      "end_time": 456676.0,
      "text": "Weird, but it is now ready to solve it, I think."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 456701.0,
      "end_time": 458112.0,
      "text": "Go and solve it."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 458818.0,
      "end_time": 463102.0,
      "text": "Yes! It is now executing symbolic computation."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 464300.0,
      "end_time": 465609.0,
      "text": "Even more weird,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 465634.0,
      "end_time": 470459.0,
      "text": "but probably this is the most fun part for the machine."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 470483.0,
      "end_time": 472834.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 472858.0,
      "end_time": 475673.0,
      "text": "Now it outputs a perfect answer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 475697.0,
      "end_time": 480404.0,
      "text": "though its proof is impossible to read, even for mathematicians."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 482773.0,
      "end_time": 489734.0,
      "text": "Anyway, last year our robot was among the top one percent"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 490199.0,
      "end_time": 493832.0,
      "text": "in the second stage written exam in mathematics."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 494652.0,
      "end_time": 497861.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 498412.0,
      "end_time": 499722.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 499747.0,
      "end_time": 502218.0,
      "text": "So, did it enter Todai?"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 502981.0,
      "end_time": 506390.0,
      "text": "No, not as I expected."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 506783.0,
      "end_time": 508182.0,
      "text": "Why?"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 508206.0,
      "end_time": 510845.0,
      "text": "Because it doesn&#39;t understand any meaning."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 512308.0,
      "end_time": 516386.0,
      "text": "Let me show you a typical error it made in the English test."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 516409.99999999994,
      "end_time": 519386.99999999994,
      "text": "[Nate: We&#39;re almost at the bookstore. Just a few more minutes."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 519412.00000000006,
      "end_time": 522451.00000000006,
      "text": "Sunil: Wait. ______ . Nate: Thank you! That always happens ...]"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 522475.0,
      "end_time": 523626.0,
      "text": "Two people are talking."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 523650.0,
      "end_time": 525704.0,
      "text": "For us, who can understand the situation --"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 525704.0,
      "end_time": 528477.0,
      "text": "[1. \"We walked for a long time.\" 2. \"We&#39;re almost there.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 528501.0,
      "end_time": 531533.0,
      "text": "3. \"Your shoes look expensive.\" 4. \"Your shoelace is untied.\"]"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 531557.0,
      "end_time": 534430.0,
      "text": "it is obvious number four is the correct answer, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 534454.0,
      "end_time": 536692.0,
      "text": "But Todai Robot chose number two,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 536716.0,
      "end_time": 542760.0,
      "text": "even after learning 15 billion English sentences"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 542100.0,
      "end_time": 544828.0,
      "text": "using deep learning technologies."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 547600.0,
      "end_time": 551772.0,
      "text": "OK, so now you might understand what I said:"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 552399.0,
      "end_time": 555470.0,
      "text": "modern AIs do not read,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 555710.0,
      "end_time": 556484.0,
      "text": "do not understand."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 557516.0,
      "end_time": 560685.0,
      "text": "They only disguise as if they do."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 564867.0,
      "end_time": 567848.0,
      "text": "This is the distribution graph"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 567872.0,
      "end_time": 573649.0,
      "text": "of half a million students who took the same exam as Todai Robot."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 574558.0,
      "end_time": 579723.0,
      "text": "Now our Todai Robot is among the top 20 percent,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 580986.0,
      "end_time": 583401.0,
      "text": "and it was capable to pass"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 583425.0,
      "end_time": 587366.0,
      "text": "more than 60 percent of the universities in Japan --"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 587390.0,
      "end_time": 588766.0,
      "text": "but not Todai."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 590116.0,
      "end_time": 594141.0,
      "text": "But see how it is beyond the volume zone"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 594165.0,
      "end_time": 597290.0,
      "text": "of to-be white-collar workers."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 600600.0,
      "end_time": 602917.0,
      "text": "You might think I was delighted."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 603939.0,
      "end_time": 607910.0,
      "text": "After all, my robot was surpassing students everywhere."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 609220.0,
      "end_time": 611713.0,
      "text": "Instead, I was alarmed."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 613860.0,
      "end_time": 618693.0,
      "text": "How on earth could this unintelligent machine outperform students --"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 618717.0,
      "end_time": 620900.0,
      "text": "our children?"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 620330.0,
      "end_time": 621186.0,
      "text": "Right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 622101.0,
      "end_time": 626503.0,
      "text": "I decided to investigate what was going on in the human world."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 628542.0,
      "end_time": 633271.0,
      "text": "I took hundreds of sentences from high school textbooks"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 633859.0,
      "end_time": 637172.0,
      "text": "and made easy multiple-choice quizzes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 637196.0,
      "end_time": 641339.0,
      "text": "and asked thousands of high school students to answer."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 642690.0,
      "end_time": 643866.0,
      "text": "Here is an example:"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 643890.0,
      "end_time": 646708.0,
      "text": "[Buddhism spread to ... , Christianity to ... and Oceania,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 646732.0,
      "end_time": 647882.0,
      "text": "and Islam to ...]"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 647907.0,
      "end_time": 650647.0,
      "text": "Of course, the original problems are written in Japanese,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 650671.0,
      "end_time": 651826.0,
      "text": "their mother tongue."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 651850.0,
      "end_time": 653365.0,
      "text": "[ ______ has spread to Oceania."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 653389.0,
      "end_time": 655806.0,
      "text": "1. Hinduism 2. Christianity 3. Islam 4. Buddhism ]"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 655830.0,
      "end_time": 658129.0,
      "text": "Obviously, Christianity is the answer, isn&#39;t it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 658153.0,
      "end_time": 659367.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s written!"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 661482.0,
      "end_time": 665507.0,
      "text": "And Todai Robot chose the correct answer, too."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 666758.0,
      "end_time": 671637.0,
      "text": "But one-third of junior high school students"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 671661.0,
      "end_time": 674272.0,
      "text": "failed to answer this question."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 676456.0,
      "end_time": 679615.0,
      "text": "Do you think it is only the case in Japan?"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 679639.0,
      "end_time": 681615.0,
      "text": "I do not think so,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 681639.0,
      "end_time": 688100.0,
      "text": "because Japan is always ranked among the top in OECD PISA tests,"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 688340.0,
      "end_time": 691961.0,
      "text": "measuring 15-year-old students&#39; performance in mathematics,"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 691985.0,
      "end_time": 693949.0,
      "text": "science and reading"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 693973.0,
      "end_time": 695608.0,
      "text": "every three years."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 699390.0,
      "end_time": 701443.0,
      "text": "We have been believing"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 701467.0,
      "end_time": 703510.0,
      "text": "that everybody can learn"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 703534.0,
      "end_time": 705439.0,
      "text": "and learn well,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 705463.0,
      "end_time": 709160.0,
      "text": "as long as we provide good learning materials"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 709184.0,
      "end_time": 710639.0,
      "text": "free on the web"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 710663.0,
      "end_time": 713732.0,
      "text": "so that they can access through the internet."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 713756.0,
      "end_time": 719615.0,
      "text": "But such wonderful materials may benefit only those who can read well,"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 720534.0,
      "end_time": 724468.0,
      "text": "and the percentage of those who can read well"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 724493.0,
      "end_time": 727871.0,
      "text": "may be much less than we expected."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 730400.0,
      "end_time": 734281.0,
      "text": "How we humans will coexist with AI"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 734305.0,
      "end_time": 737827.0,
      "text": "is something we have to think about carefully,"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 737851.0,
      "end_time": 739988.0,
      "text": "based on solid evidence."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 741630.0,
      "end_time": 745400.0,
      "text": "At the same time, we have to think in a hurry"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 745640.0,
      "end_time": 747466.0,
      "text": "because time is running out."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 748106.0,
      "end_time": 749268.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 749626.0,
      "end_time": 753559.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 754211.0,
      "end_time": 756291.0,
      "text": "Chris Anderson: Noriko, thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 756315.0,
      "end_time": 758800.0,
      "text": "Noriko Arai: Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 758104.0,
      "end_time": 763408.0,
      "text": "CA: In your talk, you so beautifully give us a sense of how AIs think,"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 763432.0,
      "end_time": 764996.0,
      "text": "what they can do amazingly"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 765200.0,
      "end_time": 766715.0,
      "text": "and what they can&#39;t do."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 766739.0,
      "end_time": 768233.0,
      "text": "But -- do I read you right,"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 768257.0,
      "end_time": 773526.0,
      "text": "that you think we really need quite an urgent revolution in education"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 773551.0,
      "end_time": 777706.0,
      "text": "to help kids do the things that humans can do better than AIs?"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 777730.0,
      "end_time": 779580.0,
      "text": "NA: Yes, yes, yes."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 779820.0,
      "end_time": 783117.0,
      "text": "Because we humans can understand the meaning."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 783141.0,
      "end_time": 788460.0,
      "text": "That is something which is very, very lacking in AI."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 788710.0,
      "end_time": 792439.0,
      "text": "But most of the students just pack the knowledge"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 792463.0,
      "end_time": 796366.0,
      "text": "without understanding the meaning of the knowledge,"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 796390.0,
      "end_time": 799199.0,
      "text": "so that is not knowledge, that is just memorizing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 799223.0,
      "end_time": 801673.0,
      "text": "and AI can do the same thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 801697.0,
      "end_time": 805328.0,
      "text": "So we have to think about a new type of education."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 805352.0,
      "end_time": 808641.0,
      "text": "CA: A shift from knowledge, rote knowledge, to meaning."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 808665.0,
      "end_time": 809815.0,
      "text": "NA: Mm-hmm."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 809840.0,
      "end_time": 813800.0,
      "text": "CA: Well, there&#39;s a challenge for the educators. Thank you so much."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 813104.0,
      "end_time": 814802.0,
      "text": "NA: Thank you very much. Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 814826.0,
      "end_time": 816110.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}